Description:	This stored procedure is a master stored procedure into which the MI Team
				can insert their own stored procedures that they have created in the BI schema. 
				This proc is executed by the "MI Automation" SQL Agent Job that is started by 
				the last step of Main Batch Tail End job.

				Note that the SQL Agent Job "MI Automation" is run under proxy account 
				SERV\SQL_MI_PROXY_USER as follows:

				sqlcmd -E -S $(ESCAPE_SQUOTE(SRVR)) -d prod_zurich_openwork_datawarehouse -Q "EXEC BI.AutomationMaster;" -b

AMENDMENT HISTORY
=================

Date		Author		Description
----		------		-----------
25/08/2021	A Groves	US54791/SP58 Quick wins: 
						1) BI.pr_WrittenBusinessCaseByCase added.
						2) TRY/CATCH and failure email added.
20/09/2021	A Groves	US57550/SP60 Quick wins:
						Added BI.pr_IssuedBusinessCaseByCase added.
24/11/2021	A Groves	SP63/US62644. Performance improvement in proc "BI.GetIssuedBusiness"
						added logging, so the logging by this proc has been removed.
20/01/2022	A Groves	SP64/US66034. Performance improvement to proc BI.pr_IssuedBusinessCaseByCase.
						This proc now accepts an additional parameter to make it run in either full
						rebuild mode or incremental update mode. It was agreed with John Homer on 
						20/01/2022, that it would run in full rebuild mode on a Sunday and on all 
