/**********************************************************************************************************
  	 Program:  	GetIssuedBusiness
  	 					
	  Author:	Original MI script from Issues Production Scan.sql

Date created:	Unknown
													
 Description:   This stored proc implements the "Issued Business" scan to populate table
				[dbo].[IssuedBusiness].

				It is called as follows:

				exec BI.GetIssuedBusiness
													
Amendment History								
