						BSC Rebate and Legacy Recurring
04/08/2022	J Homer		Change BSC Query to use the correct date
17/10/2022	J Homer		Classify Wessex product as GI instead of Protection as per Finance request
02/11/2022	J Homer		Amend the code for capturing Firm UID so that BSC is correctly allocated to 
